page.title: 09Polly's Day in Maresfield
page.content: {7.00}Got up and played with the computer. {7.45}We had breakfast with dad.I had Co_Co pops.Dad had Cornflakes and a cup of tea. {9.00}Went upstairs and got dressed {9.30}Out on my bike. {9.45}Played on swing ball. {1.00}The family had lunch.Sausages and Jacket Potatoes. {1.50}Watched Wimbledon tennis. {2.00}Went to Fairwarp Village fete {2.30}Had a pony ride. {2.45}Watched fancy dress competion {3.00}Looked at the stalls. {3.15}Had a pony ride.Then we went to my aunties house. {3.30}We went for a walk. {4.30}Spaghetti Bolognaise for tea. {7.30}Dad came and took me home. {9.00}Friends came for the evening. {10.00}I went to bed.
